		</div>
		<div class="ec-assignment-side"><div class="ec-mini-note">System assigns licences automatically when you click assign, so there is no priority field to configure in the first version.</div><div class="ec-mini-note">Recommended flow: 1) choose a key 2) filter licences 3) tick multiple items 4) click assign 5) use unassign or replace when you need to adjust the mapping.</div><div class="ec-actions compact"><button class="ec-btn ec-btn-primary" id="ecAssignSelected" style="flex:1" type="button">Assign Selected</button><button class="ec-btn ec-btn-soft" id="ecRefreshList" style="flex:1" type="button">Refresh List</button></div><div class="ec-actions compact"><button class="ec-btn ec-btn-soft" id="ecUnassignSelected" style="flex:1" type="button">Unassign Selected</button><button class="ec-btn ec-btn-soft" id="ecReplaceSelected" style="flex:1" type="button">Replace Selected</button></div></div>
